1. Make sure the version will be right (for a new minor version that means that you
   should set the patch level to -1 so dcvs will bump it to 0)

2. Write ChangeLog entry.

3. make dist, check that it builds and installs correctly.

4. CVS commit.

5. cvs tag Release_X_Y_Z

6. Sign and upload dist tarball.

7. Generate new API documentation, upload it, update the redirect page.

8. Update webpages.

9. Announce on http://freshmeat.net and any relevant mailing lists.
